title: Video: Recapping the Seattle Seahawks’ overtime loss to the Bengals
text:
Seattle Times reporter Bob Condotta talks about the Seahawks’ 27-24 overtime loss to the Bengals Sunday in Cincinnati. Check out our complete game coverage at our Seahawks Game Center .
Bob Condotta : 206-515-5699 or bcondotta@seattletimes.com ; on Twitter: @bobcondotta . Bob Condotta covers the Seahawks for the Seattle Times. He provides daily coverage of the team throughout the year.
